formJson.name: COVID-19-Starter-Set, Follow Up for Home Quarantine

concepts.COVID-19-STARTER,_DATE_OF_TEST_RESULT_6_: Date/time that a test result was obtained. This is not when the test was ordered, or when the result was given to the patient.
concepts.COVID-19-STARTER,_SELF_MONITORING_KIT_PR: Self monitoring kit procured by patient
concepts.COVID-19-STARTER,_SERUM_GLUCOSE_29_DESC: Laboratory measurement of the glucose level in the blood in mg/ml.
concepts.COVID-19-STARTER,_SEVERE_ACUTE_RESPIRATO: Severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) detected
concepts.COVID-19-STARTER,_PULSE_25_DESC: Patient pulse rate, as measured with a peripheral oximeter.
concepts.COVID-19-STARTER,_DIASTOLIC_BLOOD_PRESSU: A patient's diastolic blood pressure measurement (taken with a manual cuff in either a sitting or standing position).
concepts.COVID-19-STARTER,_ARTERIAL_BLOOD_OXYGEN_: Oxygen saturation, as measured from a peripheral oximeter.
concepts.COVID-19-STARTER,_SYSTOLIC_BLOOD_PRESSUR: A patient's systolic blood pressure measurement (taken with a manual cuff in either a sitting or standing position).
